our relationships.

10:43.276 --> 10:47.881
Well, I'll tell you
something about my wife.

10:47.915 --> 10:49.817
She could take Tyson
and the Terminator.

10:54.554 --> 10:56.323
Hey, Dan, I'm serious.

10:56.356 --> 10:57.657
Maybe we should
open up a little.

10:57.691 --> 10:59.559
