about personal things that

10:59.592 --> 11:00.828
really matter.

11:00.861 --> 11:03.396
Well, I've got
to go to the can.

11:03.430 --> 11:06.366
You can't get much
more personal than that.

11:06.399 --> 11:08.268
This is nuts, guys.

11:08.301 --> 11:09.602
I mean, we're all married.

11:09.636 --> 11:15.976
We've all got marital issues,
like money and love, sex.

11:16.009 --> 11:19.646
Did Roseanne
get a hold of you?

11:19.679 --> 11:22.015
Now take me and Jackie, for
instance, when we first got

11:22.049 --> 11:25.085
