11:25.118 --> 11:26.253
Then we went through
a period where

11:26.286 --> 11:28.555
we hardly had any sex at all.

11:28.588 --> 11:31.391
Oh, dear god.

11:31.424 --> 11:34.594
Maybe you're the only
one of you now having sex.

11:34.627 --> 11:36.263
What's that supposed to mean?

11:36.296 --> 11:38.231
