11:47.007 --> 11:48.308
Let's just drop it.

11:48.341 --> 11:52.545
I hit a little bit
too close to home, huh?

11:52.579 --> 11:53.981
Not my home.

11:54.014 --> 11:56.216
It's not my wife who said
she's not getting any.

12:01.288 --> 12:03.456
What the hell are
you talking about?

12:03.490 --> 12:08.461
