Jackie about the other night.

14:59.899 --> 15:01.568
That?

15:01.601 --> 15:04.837
Yes, that.

15:04.871 --> 15:06.773
What goes on in our
bedroom is sacred.

15:06.806 --> 15:07.807
Oh, yeah.

15:07.840 --> 15:09.542
